title: Eifert snags sixth touchdown catch in Bengals win
text:
Eifert snags sixth touchdown catch in Bengals win 
By Dean Pantazi - 21Alive Eifert snags sixth touchdown catch in Bengals win October 18, 2015 Updated Oct 18, 2015 at 10:40 PM EDT 
BUFFALO, NY (21 Alive) - Dwenger and Notre Dame grad Tyler Eifert on Sunday caught his sixth touchdown pass of the season for the Cincinnati Bengals in their 34-21 win in Buffalo. 
It was a four yard grab from Andy Dalton in the fourth quarter on a day that Eifert caught all four balls thrown to him by Dalton for 30 yards
